title: Match facts: Manchester United v Wolfsburg (UEFA Champions League) - World
text:
Related UEFA Champions League group stage results & scorers (2nd matchday) Full time: Manchester United 2-1 Wolfsburg
Scorers : Mata 34', Smalling 53'/Caligiuri 4'
Yellow cards : Schneiderlin 39', Schweinsteiger 41', Depay 62'
Starting lineups:
Manchester United: David De Gea, Daley Blind, Chris Smalling, Antonio Valencia (Ashley Young 46') , Matteo Darmian, Bastian Schweinsteiger (Phil Jones 73') , Memphis Depay (Pereira 62'), Morgan Schneiderlin , Juan Mata, Wayne Rooney , Anthony Martial
Wolfsburg: Diego Benaglio, Christian Traesch, Dante, Naldo, Ricardo Rodriguez, Daniel Caligiuri, Julian Draxler, Max Kruse, Joshua Guilavogui, Maximilian Arnold (Bendtner 70'), Bas Dost (Schurrle 70')
Venue: Old Trafford (Manchester)
Referee: V. Kassai (Hungary)
